How to set up a machine with this config:



1. Install NixOS on your machine
2. Add this to your /etc/nixos/configuration.nix:
    nix = {
    extraOptions = ''
      experimental-features = nix-command flakes
    '';
   };
3. Run 'sudo nixos-rebuild switch'
4. Enter shell with 'nix-shell -p git' and clone this repo
5. Cd into the flake config directory
6. Copy your hardware configuration into appropriate profile e.g. if using desktop, place it in desktop/ (sudo cp /etc/nixos/hardware-configuration.nix ~/[path to this repo]/desktop/)
7. Run 'sudo nixos-rebuild boot --flake .#michael' to switch to grub
8. Run 'sudo nix flake update' to update packages
9. Run 'sudo nixos-rebuild switch --flake .#michael' to apply configuration to OS

